{"tid":2113493,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周一二上班駕23號線  新巴車長染疫 19司機停工","createTime":"2020-07-18T07:17:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T07:17:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3cf508265583b7d65cac500a72bae37dd5d7487a","tid":2113493,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T07:17:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200718/6VVCEXRX2WEJ6VGVNAQRMW2XLU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200718%2F6VVCEXRX2WEJ6VGVNAQRMW2XLU%2F&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=de51c117\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200718%2F6VVCEXRX2WEJ6VGVNAQRMW2XLU%2F&h=4b0d69d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200718/6VVCEXRX2WEJ6VGVNAQRMW2XLU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n周一二上班駕23號線 <br />\n新巴車長染疫 19司機停工<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/51JJX1-Q2ynT4IEV1J1pEhIYj-4=/190x132/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NHZ6P637PXNSBJN7CG45ZJK7ZE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F51JJX1-Q2ynT4IEV1J1pEhIYj-4%3D%2F190x132%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNHZ6P637PXNSBJN7CG45ZJK7ZE.jpg&h=fe3ee79a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n確診的新巴車長負責23號線，來往北角碼頭及蒲飛路巴士總站。馬泉崇攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨日有32宗確診個案與源頭不明個案有關，部份為家庭群組。其中一名新巴司機與太太同樣確診。早前38歲入境處高級入境事務助理員染疫，其外傭昨亦確診。新巴表示，已徹底消毒確診車長所駕駛的巴士，並安排19名與確診者有接觸的員工進行檢測。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：賽馬會朗逸居院友 職員 染疫<br />\n<br />\n61歲任職新巴23號線巴士司機昨日確診，為個案1693號。他7月14日開始發燒、咳嗽及喉嚨痛，居於沙田博康邨博泰樓，沒有到過其他確診的士司機所到之處。個案1713號為其65歲太太，她在7月14日開始流鼻水、咳嗽及喉嚨痛。<br />\n<br />\n新巴表示，確診車長於7月13日至14日上班，。。。。。。。。。。車身編號3828、4062、4072、4076。四輛巴士前晚已徹底消毒清潔，包括冷氣隔塵網。<br />\n<br />\n北角碼頭巴士總站、蒲飛路巴士總站。。。。。。。。。。19人暫時停工進行病毒測試。<br />\n<br />\n翻查紀錄，確診車長曾於7月2日駕駛116號過海巴士線，來往慈雲山和鰂魚涌，及後一直駕駛23號線。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vrh5_e88pTnFSUkSl62PbWBbVm0=/623x636/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I7LFWWE6EJVFD232HTRFQS7YIQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fvrh5_e88pTnFSUkSl62PbWBbVm0%3D%2F623x636%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI7LFWWE6EJVFD232HTRFQS7YIQ.gif&h=8188c0fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n工會曾促加裝膠板被拒<br />\n<br />\n新巴職工會理事長林錦標表示，暫未知其。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心昨日亦錄得多宗家庭群組確診個案，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n入境處表示，昨午接獲衞生防護中。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n有職員表示，處理換領新身份證時需要巿民除下口罩拍照，屬高風險動作。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VVh4DJ58uOnSFF3HgQhUX-qXbdk=/1704x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PJBQEF6GSDFPOSMJMJGCXVFUMI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVVh4DJ58uOnSFF3HgQhUX-qXbdk%3D%2F1704x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPJBQEF6GSDFPOSMJMJGCXVFUMI.jpg&h=e52f1111&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n工作人員昨消毒涉事的四輛巴士。新巴提供圖片"}]}